{"tid":1904824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[高溫燒毒] 南葵涌武漢肺炎診所 疑遭縱火變電站熏黑","createTime":"2020-02-29T20:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T03:19:59.000Z","uid":200663,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"55068c311e7913a30b1475ea04c2b7a85a72b90a","tid":1904824,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T20:54:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20200301/60659137\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200301%2F60659137&d=EEQ1dbVkwObjLGYhXKOOXBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=902a9c91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200301%2F60659137&h=1867085c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20200301/60659137</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n葵盛圍南葵涌賽馬會分科診療所，凌晨1時許，街坊聽到診所傳出爆炸聲及有煙冒出<br />\n(...)<br />\n警方表示診所牆身有兩處被熏黑，地上有玻璃碎片及一個卡式石油氣罐，警員於現場檢走該些玻璃碎片及卡式石油氣罐作進一步檢驗。初步調查後相信起火原因有可疑，列作縱火案件，交由葵青警區刑事調查隊第六隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。"},{"pid":"38191d4bcba836026eae9f80344f0337b60d9cc1","tid":1904824,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T20:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a9d2825a9b21873a1f0ee72fe705e649b025fa","tid":1904824,"uid":200663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T20:56:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200301/photo/bkn-20200301020027996-0301_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200301033007\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200301%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200301020027996-0301_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200301033007&h=b4edbf50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n百份報有圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41073f9c11349c3